content: [2025, Age 22] [TextBlock(text="Tokyo taught me the power of subtle design in tech, the art of blending tradition with innovation. Now, back in NYC, I see the stark contrast in how tech shapes urban life. AI assistants are my new partners in code, and I'm learning to dance with them in this bustling digital metropolis.", type='text')]

[TextBlock(text="Just got my hands on the latest AI-driven coding tool. This thing can write code so fast, it's like watching a digital chef whip up gourmet dishes in seconds. My code is now cleaner, my bugs are fewer, and my coffee intake has doubled. Who knew AI could make me both more efficient and more caffeinated?", type='text')]
